Command: |CKBconfluence|000
Guild Level: 30

Worldroot Confluence is the Druid capstone invocation.  It braids all
four currents through you for a short time, reducing invocation costs
and improving the nwyfre momentum you gain while fighting.

While the confluence lasts, your invocations also feed your weakest
current.  This is the moment when a prepared Druid should feel like a
true ritual caster rather than a weapon fighter.
